  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511290/extras/7773f35b7b862fecbf0685e4a8b6eaaa.avif?t=1711213510\" width=620 height=160 /></span><br><br>This adventure <strong>requires 2 players</strong> to complete!<br>You <strong>cannot</strong> play this adventure alone, the game <strong>requires 2 players who own the game to play!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Red, Blue and Purple</h2>You can only touch and interact with the world in your colour! Both players can touch purple, but cannot touch each others colour.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >30 Unique Levels</h2>The game features 30 Unique levels, experimenting with different platforming challenges and ideas!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Colour-blind Support</h2>Two Cubes supports multiple types of Colour-blindness: Deuteranopia, Protanopia and Tritanopia!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511290/extras/fdeb6c9b85d9e5306a4af9cbad811cd2.avif?t=1711213510\" width=620 height=160 /></span>",
